{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/joomla-module-parameter/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Über <a href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Parameter_(Informatik)\">Parameter</a> ist das Joomla-Modul für Endbenutzer flexibel anpassbar. Parameter sind Übergabewerte, durch die Joomla auf die Verarbeitung bestimmter Werte eingestellt wird. Anders ausgedrückt sind Parameter programmextern gesetzte Einflussfaktoren. Sie werden verwendet, um Joomla von außen mitzuteilen, welche Daten wie verarbeitet werden sollen.</p>\n<h2>Für Ungeduldige</h2>\n<p>Sieh dir den geänderten Programmcode in der <a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t32...t33\">Diff-Ansicht</a><sup id=\"fnref-github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t32...t33\"><a href=\"#fn-github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t32...t33\" class=\"footnote-ref\">github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t32...t33</a></sup> an und übernimm diese Änderungen in deine Entwicklungsversion.</p>\n<h2>Schritt für Schritt</h2>\n<p>In diesem Abschnitt fügen wir Parameter zum Modul hinzu.</p>\n<p>In der nachfolgenden Übersicht sind die neu hinzugekommenen Dateien mit einem Hintergrund versehen und die geänderten umrandet.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/202f8809799ad55b88bf449183adfbd9/90804/tree33.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 84.81012658227847%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Übersicht über die in diesem Kapitel bearbeiteten Dateien\"\n        title=\"Übersicht über die in diesem Kapitel bearbeiteten Dateien\"\n        src=\"/static/202f8809799ad55b88bf449183adfbd9/f058b/tree33.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/202f8809799ad55b88bf449183adfbd9/c26ae/tree33.png 158w,\n/static/202f8809799ad55b88bf449183adfbd9/6bdcf/tree33.png 315w,\n/static/202f8809799ad55b88bf449183adfbd9/f058b/tree33.png 630w,\n/static/202f8809799ad55b88bf449183adfbd9/40601/tree33.png 945w,\n/static/202f8809799ad55b88bf449183adfbd9/78612/tree33.png 1260w,\n/static/202f8809799ad55b88bf449183adfbd9/90804/tree33.png 3733w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Neue Dateien</h3>\n<p>In diesem Teil wurden lediglich Dateien geändert. Es gibt keine neuen Dateien.</p>\n<h3>Geänderte Dateien</h3>\n<h4>Modul</h4>\n<h5><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t32...t33#diff-9c4225bbdf2ea51af1036568f0f1e8817ecc47e86d001366d2278a2e7281281a\">modules/mod<em>foo/language/en-GB/en-GB.mod</em>foo.ini</a></h5>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/blob/b8c783812c9acf66a6c0c0a534d5d43b987510c5/src/modules/mod_foo/language/en-GB/en-GB.mod_foo.ini\">modules/mod<em>foo/language/en-GB/en-GB.mod</em>foo.ini</a></p>\n<p>Die Beschriftung des Parameters soll sich an die aktive Sprache anpassen. Aus diesem Grund nutzen wir die Sprachdatei.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Wunderst du dich über den Präfix <code class=\"language-text\">COM_</code> in <code class=\"language-text\">COM_MODULES_FOOPARAMS_FIELDSET_LABEL</code>? Der Sprachstring wird von Joomla automatisch erstellt, weil ein Fieldset mit dem Namen <code class=\"language-text\">fooparams</code> hinzukommt.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container grvsc-has-line-highlighting solarized-light\" data-language=\"php\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">MOD_FOO</span><span class=\"mtk8\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;[PROJECT_NAME]&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">MOD_FOO_XML_DESCRIPTION</span><span class=\"mtk8\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;Foo Module&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">MOD_FOO_FIELD_URL_LABEL</span><span class=\"mtk8\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;URL&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">COM_MODULES_FOOPARAMS_FIELDSET_LABEL</span><span class=\"mtk8\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;Foo Parameter&quot;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h5><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t32...t33#diff-43348bdc6a37cd697897d234acd68a56c191ded22f30b54aa8de2e9c099b9c84\">modules/mod<em>foo/ mod</em>foo.php</a></h5>\n<p>In der Einstiegsdatei des Moduls <code class=\"language-text\">modules/mod_foo/ mod_foo.php</code> prüfen wir, auf welchen Wert der Parameter gesetzt ist und speichern ihn in eine Variable. So ist später ein unkompliziertes Zugreifen möglich.</p>\n<p><a href=\"\">modules/mod<em>foo/ mod</em>foo.php</a></p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container grvsc-has-line-highlighting solarized-light\" data-language=\"php\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk8\">$</span><span class=\"mtk7\">test</span><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk8\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">FooHelper::</span><span class=\"mtk7\">getText</span><span class=\"mtk1\">();</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk8\">$</span><span class=\"mtk7\">url</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">=</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">$</span><span class=\"mtk7\">params</span><span class=\"mtk8\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">get</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&#39;domain&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">require</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">ModuleHelper::</span><span class=\"mtk7\">getLayoutPath</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&#39;mod_foo&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk8\">$</span><span class=\"mtk7\">params</span><span class=\"mtk8\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">get</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&#39;layout&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">, </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&#39;default&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">));</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h5><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t32...t33#diff-c111dcc16cb14017dbacf97ab7d495ac6e7225b2b2097774adc23a977d5cc3c3\">modules/mod<em>foo/ mod</em>foo.xml</a></h5>\n<p>Im Manifest fügen wir den neuen Paramter hinzu, so dass dieser im Joomla Backend bearbeitbar ist.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/blob/b8c783812c9acf66a6c0c0a534d5d43b987510c5/src/modules/mod_foo/mod_foo.xml\">modules/mod<em>foo/ mod</em>foo.xml</a></p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container grvsc-has-line-highlighting solarized-light\" data-language=\"php\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> \t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">folder</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">language</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">folder</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> \t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">filename</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">mod_foo</span><span class=\"mtk8\">.</span><span class=\"mtk4\">xml</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">filename</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> \t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">files</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">config</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">fields</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">name</span><span class=\"mtk8\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;params&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">fieldset</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">name</span><span class=\"mtk8\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;fooparams&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">field</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t\t\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk4\">name</span><span class=\"mtk8\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;domain&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t\t\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk4\">type</span><span class=\"mtk8\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;url&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t\t\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk4\">label</span><span class=\"mtk8\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;MOD_FOO_FIELD_URL_LABEL&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t\t\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk4\">filter</span><span class=\"mtk8\">=</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&quot;url&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">/&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">fieldset</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">fields</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">\t</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">config</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">extension</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Verwende <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;fieldset name=&quot;basic&quot;&gt;</code>. um die Parameter im ersten sich unmittelbar öffnenden Tabulator anzuzeigen.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Neben den Parametern, die ein Entwickler in sein Modul einfügt, gib es Standardparameter, die Joomla selbst handhabt. Zum Beispiel <code class=\"language-text\">/administrator/components/com_modules/forms/advanced.xml</code>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/191e2/j4x38x1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.10126582278481%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Joomla Modul Parameter\"\n        title=\"Joomla Modul Parameter\"\n        src=\"/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/f058b/j4x38x1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/c26ae/j4x38x1.png 158w,\n/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/6bdcf/j4x38x1.png 315w,\n/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/f058b/j4x38x1.png 630w,\n/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/40601/j4x38x1.png 945w,\n/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/78612/j4x38x1.png 1260w,\n/static/5f12493d39232a592c68ee52605cde3e/191e2/j4x38x1.png 1836w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h5><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t32...t33#diff-5dc488d0a39079a73583a37bf1b465fcf99ca183970958084a2eac52f723a4ba\">modules/mod_foo/tmpl/default.php</a></h5>\n<p>In der moduleigenen Template-Datei könne wir nun auf den Wert des Parameters zugreifen. Im nachfolgenden Beispiel geben wir den Wert als Text aus. Meist wird ein Parameter in einer komplexeren Art verwendet, zum Beispiel innerhalb von Kontrollstrukturen wie If-Anweisungen oder Schleifen.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Ein Beispiel für die komplexere Anwendung eines Parameters ist eine digitale Landkarte, auf der anhand von Parametern Steuerelemente wie <code class=\"language-text\">Lokalisiere mich</code> oder eine Auswahl des Kartentyps ermöglicht wird.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/blob/b8c783812c9acf66a6c0c0a534d5d43b987510c5/src/modules/mod_foo/tmpl/default.php\">modules/mod_foo/tmpl/default.php</a></p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container grvsc-has-line-highlighting solarized-light\" data-language=\"php\" data-index=\"3\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> \\</span><span class=\"mtk7\">defined</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk11\">&#39;_JEXEC&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">) </span><span class=\"mtk8\">or</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">die</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-del\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-del\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"-\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk9\">echo</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&#39;[PROJECT_NAME]&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">.</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">$</span><span class=\"mtk7\">test</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line grvsc-line-diff grvsc-line-diff-add\"><span class=\"grvsc-gutter-pad\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-gutter grvsc-diff-add\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-content=\"+\"></span><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk9\">echo</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&#39;[PROJECT_NAME]&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">.</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">$</span><span class=\"mtk7\">test</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">.</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">&#39;&lt;br /&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">.</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">$</span><span class=\"mtk7\">url</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2>Teste dein Joomla-Module</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Installiere das Modul in Joomla Version 4, um es zu testen:</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Kopiere die Dateien im <code class=\"language-text\">modules</code> Ordner in den <code class=\"language-text\">modules</code> Ordner deiner Joomla 4 Installation.</p>\n<p>Eine neue Installation ist nicht erforderlich. Verwende die aus dem vorhergehenden Teil weiter.</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Überprüfe das Vorhandensein des Parameters im Backend.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9145b9ad6e8b0e23038a1a9d684246c4/f2b95/j4x38x4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.139240506329116%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Joomla Modul testen\"\n        title=\"Joomla Modul testen\"\n        src=\"/static/9145b9ad6e8b0e23038a1a9d684246c4/f058b/j4x38x4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9145b9ad6e8b0e23038a1a9d684246c4/c26ae/j4x38x4.png 158w,\n/static/9145b9ad6e8b0e23038a1a9d684246c4/6bdcf/j4x38x4.png 315w,\n/static/9145b9ad6e8b0e23038a1a9d684246c4/f058b/j4x38x4.png 630w,\n/static/9145b9ad6e8b0e23038a1a9d684246c4/40601/j4x38x4.png 945w,\n/static/9145b9ad6e8b0e23038a1a9d684246c4/78612/j4x38x4.png 1260w,\n/static/9145b9ad6e8b0e23038a1a9d684246c4/f2b95/j4x38x4.png 1515w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Überzeuge dich davon, dass der Wert des Paramete